---
title: Seared Steak & Mustardy Crushed Potatoes with Garlic Butter & Parmesan-Pear Salad
description: Tonight, sit back and enjoy the delights of 'meat and three' with a hint of Dijon mustard in the crushed potatoes to pleasantly
surprise the tastebuds. Served with seared beef rump, drizzled with garlic butter, plus crisp salad leaves, it's a many-hit-wonder.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
